des: Dry Cleaning and Laundry becomes easier with pickup and delivery dry cleaning and laundry services. Just say 'Alexa, open Sudsies Cleaners' to get started! Now you can tell Sudsies Cleaners you are on your way so they can have your clothes ready by the time you get there! Just say, 'Alexa, tell Sudsies Cleaners I am on my way' to let Sudsies Cleaners know you are on your way!
